snippet.title: Gourdlets | Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
🌈 Get it on steam NOW! http://s.team/a/2013730
💬 discord! https://discord.gg/xYgv78Azwe
💌 fan mailing list! https://forms.gle/HyTQ2ArH6CYgasqv6

Gourdlets is an easygoing sandbox game about building towns for cute vegetable folks. Create your perfect community then watch as the gourdlets make themselves at home. No objectives, no points, just good vibes. Play in full screen, or let your gourdlets hang out at the bottom of your screen!
